<div id="contact">
    <h2 class="text-center">Контакты</h2>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-5">
            <p>Свяжитесь с нами, мы ответим Вам в течение 24 часов.</p>
            <p><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-map-marker"></span> Кишинев, Молдова</p>
            <p><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-phone"></span> +373 68 032 185</p>
            <p><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-envelope"></span> dotanastea@mail.ru</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-7 slideanim">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-6 form-group">
                    <input class="form-control" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Имя" type="text" required>
